name: Julieta Rada
description:
'''Julieta Rada Jodara''' (born 25 May 1990) is a Uruguayan-Argentine singer, songwriter and television personality.

Coming from a family of musicians, she began singing in her teens. She released her debut album in 2012 and in 2015 she was nominated for the [[Latin Grammy Award for Best New Artist]]. Since 2023 she serves as a coach on ''[[La Voz Kids (Uruguayan TV series)|La Voz Kids Uruguay]].''
